All recipes are developed with vets and are AAFCO complete and balanced for all life stages and all sizes. Feeding & transition instructions included within your delivered box. Roughly 5 weeks of food for a 25Lb adult dog. This large variety box includes 6Lbs of Chicken & Sweet Potato & 3Lbs of Beef & Berries.

